description.en:
ZED RUN is a provably fair NFT-based digital horse racing game built on blockchain technology.

The ZED Token is a token that exists on the Ethereum and Polygon blockchains. It will act as the utility and in-game currency for the ZED RUN game and will bring play to earn capability.
